                                "byte_start": 81774,
                                "byte_stop": 101732,
                                "text": "The opinion of the court in two cases will be announced by Justice O\u0027Connor."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 4.981,
                        "stop": 188.552,
                        "byte_start": 101732,
